    <section id="id22956393">
      <title>DRAMA: The soap opera</title>
      <para id="id22851710">With this module we shall be looking at a medium most of you enjoy and know very well: television - specifically the ‘soap opera’.</para>
      <para id="id20571001">Television is a very intimate medium. The characters are in your living room – a close-up!</para>
      <para id="id18362089">The best known of all programmes is, undoubtedly, the serialised drama, often called a ‘soap opera’ or ‘soapie’, because in the early days many had a soap company as their sponsor.</para>
    </section>
