      <para id="id22903709">Complete the questionnaire (copies will be handed out) after the class discussion.</para>
      <para id="id19240900">1. Do you like watching television? Why? Why not?</para>
      <para id="id19443510"/>
      <para id="id19443513"/>
      <para id="id18530809"/>
      <para id="id11321426"/>
      <para id="id11321430">2. Do you like watching soap operas? Why? Name them. Why not? </para>
      <para id="id22712565"/>
      <para id="id21981690"/>
      <para id="id21981694"/>
      <para id="id22618412"/>
      <para id="id14359355">3. What was the focus of the soapie episode?</para>
