      <para id="id23008572"/>
      <para id="id22845846"/>
      <para id="id22845850">4. Did the tension work effectively in this episode to engage your desire to know what would happen next? How?</para>
      <para id="id22790946"/>
      <para id="id22777892"/>
      <para id="id22777896"/>
      <para id="id23013574"/>
      <para id="id22978725">5. What other choices could particular characters in the soapie have made?</para>
